{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/cheatsheet/23-03-11/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>IDE keyboard shortcuts л¶Җн„°, vim, shell, tmux л“ұ к°ңл°ңмһҗл“Өмқҙ мһҗмЈј мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳлҠ” нҲҙмқҳ нҺёлҰ¬н•ң кё°лҠҘл“Өм—җ лҢҖн•ҙ кё°лЎқн•©лӢҲлӢӨ. нҳ‘м—… кҙҖл Ё м°ёкі н•  мҲҳ мһҲлҠ” кё°лҠҘмқҙлӮҳ conventionлҸ„ кё°лЎқн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.  мһҳ м„ӨлӘ…лҗҳм–ҙмһҲлҠ” лё”лЎңк·ё кёҖмқҙлӮҳ мһҗлЈҢл“ӨмқҖ л§ҒнҒ¬лЎң кіөмң н•ҳмҳҖмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.  мғҲлЎң м•ҢкІҢлҗҳлҠ” лӮҙмҡ©мқҙ мғқкёё л•Ң л§ҲлӢӨ кі„мҶҚн•ҙм„ң лӮҙмҡ©мқ„ м¶”к°Җн•ҳкі  мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"pycharm\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pycharm\" aria-label=\"pycharm permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Pycharm</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ B</code>: declaration or usage search. м ңмқј мң мҡ©н•ҳлӢӨкі  мғқк°ҒлҗҳлҠ” лӢЁм¶•нӮӨ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ -</code>: expand лҗҳм–ҙ мһҲлҠ” мҪ”л“ңмқҳ нҠ№м • л¶Җл¶„мқ„ collapse</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ +</code>: collapse лҗҳм–ҙ мһҲлҠ” мҪ”л“ңмқҳ нҠ№м • л¶Җл¶„мқ„ expand</li>\n<li>Structure (<code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ 7</code>): нҢҢмқј кө¬мЎ°лҘј н•ң лҲҲм—җ л№ лҘҙкІҢ нҢҢм•…н•  мҲҳ мһҲлҠ” кё°лҠҘ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҮ§ вҮ§</code>: м „мІҙ кІҖмғү</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ E</code>: мөңк·јм—җ мӮ¬мҡ©н•ң нҢҢмқј</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҘ Enter</code>: pycharmмқҳ м ңм•ҲмӮ¬н•ӯ нҷ•мқё</li>\n<li>к°ҖлҒ” debugging мӢңм—җ лӮҙл¶Җ лқјмқҙлёҢлҹ¬лҰ¬лЎң step in мһҳ м•ҲлҗҳлҠ” кІҪмҡ° мһҲлҠ”лҚ°, мқҙлҹ° кІҪмҡ°лҠ” лҢҖл¶Җл¶„ .idea нҸҙлҚ” мӮӯм ңн•ҙм„ң мәҗмӢң м—Ҷм• л©ҙ мһҳ мһ‘лҸҷн•Ё</li>\n<li>Pycharm remote debugging in a docker container: <a href=\"https://seongwoopark.github.io/2017-06-02-study-pycharm_interpreter/\">нҢҢмқҙм°ём—җм„ң DOCKERлҘј мқҙмҡ©н•ң л””лІ„к№… нҷҳкІҪ кө¬м¶•</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"vscode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vscode\" aria-label=\"vscode permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>VSCode</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ вҮ§ P</code>: open the command palette</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ вҮ§ D</code>: open debugging tab</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ вҮ§ E</code>: open the project tab</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ вҢҘ up/down</code>: multiple cursors</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ D</code>: multiple selection</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ P</code>: search file by name</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ P + @</code>: <code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ F</code> ліҙлӢӨ лҚ” к°„нҺёнһҲ нҢҢмқј лӮҙ мҪ”л“ң кІҖмғү к°ҖлҠҘ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ вҮ§ .</code>: <code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ P + @</code>мҷҖ мң мӮ¬н•ң кё°лҠҘ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ G</code>: go to line number</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ L</code>: highlight line</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ /</code>: comment</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ N</code>: open a new file</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҘ up/down</code>: move a line</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҢҳ ></code>: vscodeмқҳ м ңм•ҲмӮ¬н•ӯ нҷ•мқё</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">вҮ§ вҢҘ F</code>: auto-formatting</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"debugging\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#debugging\" aria-label=\"debugging permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Debugging</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>launch.json нҢҢмқјмқ„ нҶөн•ҙм„ң л””лІ„к№… мҳөм…ҳ м„Өм • к°ҖлҠҘ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">name</code>: л””лІ„к№… configмқҳ мқҙлҰ„</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">type</code>: л””лІ„кұ° мң нҳ•</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">request</code>: launch or attach</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">cwd</code>: project working directory</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">program</code>: run a script</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">args</code>: command line arguments</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">env</code>: environment variables</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">console</code>: мӮ¬мҡ©н•  console мў…лҘҳ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">justMyCode</code>: falseмӢң лӮҙл¶Җ лқјмқҙлёҢлҹ¬лҰ¬ к№Ңм§ҖлҸ„ jump-in к°ҖлҠҘ</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># Example code\n{\n    \"version\": \"0.2.0\",\n    \"configurations\": [\n\n        {\n            \"name\": \"debugging option 1\",\n            \"type\": \"python\",\n            \"request\": \"launch\",\n            \"cwd\":\"${workspaceFolder}/project_dir\",\n            \"program\": \"${workspaceFolder}/project_dir/main.py\",\n            \"args\": [\n                \"--config\", \"configs/base.yaml\",\n                \"--mode\", \"train\",\n            ],\n            \"env\": {\n                \"CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES\": \"0, 1, 2\",\n            },\n            \"console\": \"integratedTerminal\",\n            \"justMyCode\": false\n        },\n\n    ]\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h5 id=\"extensions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#extensions\" aria-label=\"extensions permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Extensions</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Image: image preview, python image preview</li>\n<li>Formatter: black formatter, ...</li>\n<li>Debug: Python Test Explorer</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"vim\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vim\" aria-label=\"vim permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vim</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://vim.rtorr.com/lang/ko\">Vim cheat sheet</a></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">dd</code>: н•ң мӨ„ мһҳлқјлӮҙкё°</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">j</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">k</code>: н•ң мӨ„ лӢЁмң„мқҳ м»Өм„ң мқҙлҸҷ</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"iterm2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#iterm2\" aria-label=\"iterm2 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>iTerm2</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>н”Ңлҹ¬к·ёмқё м Ғмҡ©н•ҳл Өл©ҙ <code class=\"language-text\">.zshrc</code> нҢҢмқјмқҳ <code class=\"language-text\">plugins=()</code>м—җ н”Ңлҹ¬к·ёмқё мқҙлҰ„ м Ғм–ҙл„Јмңјл©ҙ лҗЁ\n<ul>\n<li>zsh-syntax-highlighting\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git <span class=\"token variable\">${ZSH_CUSTOM<span class=\"token operator\">:-</span>~<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>.oh-my-zsh<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>custom}</span>/plugins/zsh-syntax-highlighting</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>zsh-autosuggestions\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions <span class=\"token variable\">${ZSH_CUSTOM<span class=\"token operator\">:-</span>~<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>.oh-my-zsh<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>custom}</span>/plugins/zsh-autosuggestions</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>autojump: <code class=\"language-text\">brew install autojump</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>dotenvлқјлҠ” лӮҙмһҘ н”Ңлҹ¬к·ёмқё мЎҙмһ¬н•ҳлҠ”лҚ°, н•ҙлӢ№ н”Ңлҹ¬к·ёмқё мӮ¬мҡ©мӢң <code class=\"language-text\">~/.env</code> нҢҢмқјм—җ нҷҳкІҪліҖмҲҳ м„Өм • к°ҖлҠҘн•ҳл©° мқҙ л•Ң exportлҠ” м Ғм§Җ м•Ҡм•„лҸ„ лҗЁ</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"linux\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#linux\" aria-label=\"linux permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Linux</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/LeCoupa/awesome-cheatsheets/blob/master/languages/bash.sh\">LeCoupa / awesome-cheatsheets</a></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">env</code>: м „м—ӯ ліҖмҲҳ м„Өм • л°Ҹ мЎ°нҡҢ(л’Өм—җ к°’ мһ…л Ҙн•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ” кІҪмҡ°)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;&lt; 'TEXT'</code> <code class=\"language-text\">'TEXT'</code>: Bash multiline comment. л‘ҳ мӮ¬мқҙм—җ лӮҙмҡ©мқ„ мһ…л Ҙн•ҳл©ҙ лҗЁ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">pkill -f \"process name\"</code>: grepмқ„ нҶөн•ҙ н•ҳлӮҳм”© PIDлҘј нҷ•мқён•  н•„мҡ” м—Ҷмқҙ, н•ң лІҲм—җ processлҘј kill н•  мҲҳ мһҲмқҢ</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"task-scheduling\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#task-scheduling\" aria-label=\"task scheduling permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Task Scheduling</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">at {time}</code> <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+D</code>: commandлҘј timeм—җ мӢӨн–ү. timeмқҳ нҳ•нғңлҠ” <code class=\"language-text\">now+{num} [minutes, hours, days]</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">HH:MM YYYY-MM-DD</code> л“ұмқҙ к°ҖлҠҘ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">at -f {file_name} {time}</code>: fileмқ„ timeм—җ мӢӨн–ү</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">atq</code>: мҳҲм•Ҫлҗҳм–ҙ мһҲлҠ” мһ‘м—… лӘ©лЎқ нҷ•мқё</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">atrm {task_num}</code>: мҳҲм•Ҫлҗң мһ‘м—…мқ„ м ңкұ°</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"cpu-limit\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cpu-limit\" aria-label=\"cpu limit permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CPU Limit</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">taskset -c 0-3 python script.py</code>: CPU cores 0~3л§Ңмқ„ мӮ¬мҡ©</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">cpulimit -p \"$(pgrep -f ${file_name})\" -l 50</code>: file_name мӢӨн–үн•ҳкё° мң„н•ҙ CPU 50%л§Ң мӮ¬мҡ©</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"nvidia\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nvidia\" aria-label=\"nvidia permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>NVIDIA</h3>\n<p>nvidia-smiм—җм„ң smiлҠ” system management interfaceмқҳ м•Ҫмһҗ. Official documentлҠ” <a href=\"https://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/DCGM/docs/nvidia-smi-367.38.pdf\">мқҙ кіі</a> м°ёкі .</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">nvidia-smi -pl 150</code>: power limitмқ„ 150WмңјлЎң м„Өм •</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">nvidia-smi -lmc 6500</code>: lmcлҠ” lock memory clockмқҳ м•Ҫмһҗ. memory clock frequencyлҘј 6500 MHzмңјлЎң м ңн•ң</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">nvidia-smi -lgc 0,1800</code>: lgcлҠ” lock gpu clockмқҳ м•Ҫмһҗ. minGpuClock=0, maxGpuClock=1800мңјлЎң м„Өм •</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"network\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#network\" aria-label=\"network permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Network</h3>\n<h5 id=\"ssh-tunneling\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ssh-tunneling\" aria-label=\"ssh tunneling permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SSH Tunneling</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">ssh -L local_port:remote_server:remote_port remote_username@remote_server</code></li>\n<li>ssh -Lмқ„ нҶөн•ң н„°л„җл§Ғмқ„ нҶөн•ҙ, localм—җм„ң remote serverм—җ мӢӨн–үмӨ‘мқё м„ңл№„мҠӨм—җ мҡ”мІӯмқ„ ліҙлӮҙкі  мқ‘лӢөмқ„ л°ӣмқ„ мҲҳ мһҲмқҢ</li>\n<li>мҳҲлҘј л“Өм–ҙ, (remote serverм—җ лҢҖн•ҙ ssh_configм—җ server1мңјлЎң м„Өм •н•ҙл‘җм—ҲлӢӨкі  н•ҳкі ) server1мқҳ host 0.0.0.0(лӘЁл“  м ‘к·ј н—Ҳмҡ©), port 5000м—җ нҠ№м • APIлҘј лқ„мӣҢ л‘җм—ҲлӢӨкі  к°Җм •. к·ёлҹ¬л©ҙ <code class=\"language-text\">ssh -L 8080:0.0.0.0:5000 server1</code>мңјлЎң н„°л„җл§Ғ нӣ„, localмқҳ мӣ№ лёҢлқјмҡ°м Җм—җм„ң <a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/\">http://127.0.0.1:8080/</a> м ‘мҶҚ к°ҖлҠҘн•ҳл©° мҡ”мІӯ ліҙлӮҙкё°лҸ„ к°ҖлҠҘ</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"ssh-agent-forwarding\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ssh-agent-forwarding\" aria-label=\"ssh agent forwarding permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SSH-Agent Forwarding</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># м•„лһҳ мһ‘м—…мқ„ мҲҳн–үн•ҳкё° м „м—җ лЁјм Җ ssh public keyлҘј к№ғн—ҷм—җ л“ұлЎқн•ҙм•јн•Ё\nssh-add -K &lt;Path to key file>\nssh-add --apple-use-keychain &lt;path to key file>\t# in MacOS\nssh-add -L\t# check key</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>м„ңлІ„ м ‘мҶҚмӢң agent forwarding нҷңмҡ©н•ҳлҠ” л°©лІ•мқҖ м•„лһҳ л‘җ к°Җм§Җ мЎҙмһ¬ (нӣ„мһҗк°Җ лҚ” нҺён•Ё)</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">ssh -A &lt;username>@&lt;host></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># ~/.ssh/config\nHost &lt;host>\n   ForwardAgent yes</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">ssh -T git@github.com</code> commandлҘј нҶөн•ҙ ssh-agent forwarding м Ғмҡ©лҗҳм—ҲлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё</li>\n<li>м¶”к°Җм ҒмңјлЎң, м„ңлІ„ лӮҙ .ssh/authorized_keysм—җ н•ҙлӢ№ public keyлҘј л“ұлЎқн•ҙл‘җл©ҙ нҢЁмҠӨмӣҢл“ң мһ…л Ҙ м—ҶмқҙлҸ„ м ‘мҶҚ л°”лЎң к°ҖлҠҘн•ҳм—¬ л§Өмҡ° к°„нҺён•Ё</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"tmux\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tmux\" aria-label=\"tmux permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>tmux</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://tmuxcheatsheet.com\">Tmux Cheat Sheet &#x26; Quick Reference</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/MohamedAlaa/2961058\">MohamedAlaa / tmux-cheatsheet.markdown</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"session\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#session\" aria-label=\"session permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Session</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">tmux</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">tmux new</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">tmux new -s м„ём…ҳмқҙлҰ„</code>: session мғқм„ұ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">tmux kill-session -t м„ём…ҳмқҙлҰ„</code>: session мӮӯм ң</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">tmux kill-session -a</code>: нҳ„мһ¬ session м ңмҷё лӘЁл‘җ мӮӯм ң</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">tmux kill-session -a -t м„ём…ҳмқҙлҰ„</code>: нҠ№м • session м ңмҷё лӘЁл‘җ мӮӯм ң</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">$</code>: session мқҙлҰ„ ліҖкІҪ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">tmux ls</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">s</code>: лӘЁл“  session нҷ•мқё</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">tmux a</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">tmux a -t м„ём…ҳмқҙлҰ„</code>: sessionм—җ attach</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">d</code>: sessionм—җ detach</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">(</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">)</code>: session мқҙлҸҷ</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"window\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#window\" aria-label=\"window permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Window</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">tmux new -s м„ём…ҳмқҙлҰ„ -n мңҲлҸ„мҡ°мқҙлҰ„</code>: session мқҙлҰ„, window мқҙлҰ„мқ„ м„Өм •н•ҳм—¬ session мғқм„ұ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">c</code>: window мғқм„ұ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">,</code>: window мқҙлҰ„ ліҖкІҪ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">&amp;</code>: window лӢ«кё°</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">p</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">n</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">0~9</code>: window мқҙлҸҷ</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"pane\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pane\" aria-label=\"pane permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Pane</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">%</code>: split vertically</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">\"</code>: split horizontally</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">л°©н–ҘнӮӨ</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">0~9</code>: pane мқҙлҸҷ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">!</code>: paneмқ„ windowлЎң м „нҷҳ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b+л°©н–ҘнӮӨ</code>: pane нҒ¬кё° ліҖкІҪ</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+b</code> <code class=\"language-text\">x</code>: pane лӢ«кё°</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"collaboration\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#collaboration\" aria-label=\"collaboration permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Collaboration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Code formatter: <strong>black, flake8, yapf, pre-commit</strong>. IDE м—°лҸҷлҗҳлҠ” кІҪмҡ°м—җ, м—°лҸҷн•ҙм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳл©ҙ нҺёлҰ¬</li>\n<li>Type checker: <strong>mypy, pyright, pyre-check</strong>. IDE м—°лҸҷлҗҳлҠ” кІҪмҡ°м—җ, м—°лҸҷн•ҙм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳл©ҙ нҺёлҰ¬</li>\n<li>Commit convention: <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/blob/22b96b9/CONTRIBUTING.md#-commit-message-guidelines\">angular / angular</a>, <a href=\"https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/\">Conventional Commits</a></li>\n<li>Branch naming: <a href=\"https://nvie.com/posts/a-successful-git-branching-model/\">Vincent Driessen, A successful Git branching model</a></li>\n<li>Issue and PR template: <a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/communities/using-templates-to-encourage-useful-issues-and-pull-requests/about-issue-and-pull-request-templates\">About issue and pull request templates</a></li>\n<li>Documentation (Github wiki): <a href=\"ht